        "content": "## 🟪 VISUAL CARD GENERATION\n\n**Input Data:**\n- `{{ $json.name }}` - Candidate name\n- `{{ $json.role }}` - Job role/title\n- `{{ $json.skills }}` - Skills list\n- `{{ $json.email }}` - Verified email\n\n"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
